<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Rendiciones pendientes de aprobacion contable</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #f4f7f6; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .logo { max-width: 150px; height: auto; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .heading { color: #1e293b; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .info-box { background-color: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-box p { margin: 0; color: #1e40af; }
    .count-badge { display: inline-block; background-color: #3b82f6; color: #fff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 12px 0; }
    .report-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 20px 0; }
    .report-item { padding: 12px 14px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .report-collab { font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; }
    .report-title { color: #475569; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 2px; }
    .report-deadline { color: #dc2626; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 4px; }
    .btn-container { text-align: center; margin-top: 28px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Viatika" class="logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="heading">Rendiciones pendientes de aprobacion contable</h1>
      <p>Estimado/a <strong>{{recipientName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Las siguientes rendiciones ya fueron aprobadas por coordinacion y estan esperando <strong>tu aprobacion final</strong>:</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>{{pendingCount}} rendicion(es)</strong> pendiente(s) de aprobacion contable.</p>
      </div>

      <ul class="report-list">
        {{#each reports}}
        <li class="report-item">
          <div class="report-collab">{{this.collaboratorName}}</div>
          <div class="report-title">{{this.title}}</div>
          {{#if this.endDateFormatted}}
          <div class="report-deadline">Vence: {{this.endDateFormatted}}</div>
          {{/if}}
        </li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>

      <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="{{platformUrl}}" class="btn">Ir a la plataforma</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Viatika. Este es un recordatorio automatico.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
